# Re-include the new launcher scripts and the live-copilot smoke harness.
# They don't match the SETUP_*.command / *_test.sh patterns above, but
# being explicit prevents future accidental ignores.
!START_TEP_COPILOT.command
!STOP_TEP_COPILOT.command
!scripts/smoke_live_copilot.sh

# These knowledge-base files happen to match patterns far up in this file
# (*_REFERENCE*.md, etc.). Negations must come AFTER the patterns they
# override — last matching rule wins — so we re-include them here at the
# very bottom rather than next to the RAG/* exclude.
!RAG/converted_markdown/2_TEP_Complete_Technical_Reference.md

# AI Discovery Workbench derived caches (~30 MB). Regenerated on first use:
#   mp_archive.npz   ← pattern_tools._build_archive()
#   chroma/          ← vector_knowledge.build_or_load_index()
#   bm25_corpus.json ← vector_knowledge.build_or_load_index()
# Rebuild cost: ~3 min NIM embedding pass + ~1 min matrix-profile archive build.
backend/data/embeddings/

# Eval result artifacts are derived from the eval scripts; keep the scripts in
# git, leave the JSONs / markdown reports / synthetic cases out so the repo
# doesn't carry stale numbers across re-runs.
backend/evaluation/results/*.json
backend/evaluation/results/*.md

